Titania is in an very early development state. That mean only a subset of the VRML standard is currently working. A full list of implemented node types will comming soon. JavaScript is enabled by default. The VRML standard of the JavaScript implementation is supported.
Although Titania aims to provide the full VRML standard for version 1.0 some X3D node types will be supported too. This includes LayerSet, Layer and OrthoViewpoint.
